    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may create bright light that covers an area in confusing colors and designs. All squares in the area of this bright light are considered difficult terrain.</p>\n<p>By spending a spell point you can make the patterns of the bright light even more intricate and confusing. Each round a creature is within the area, it must attempt a Will save or fall prone.</p>\n<p>Blind creatures (or creatures that have closed their eyes for at least 1 round) and creatures that do not rely on sight are immune to the effects of this talent.</p>\n",
